{"tid":1819804,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求搏炒","createTime":"2020-01-11T06:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T05:22:12.000Z","uid":226082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"015273ced51fe2d037dee0c7219509febab62bfa","tid":1819804,"uid":226082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"借acct<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我公司開咗10年，<br />\n但我係公司做左10個月，已經係我個post有史以來做得最長果位同事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公司九成以上嘅員工，做咗一年內都會辭職或者俾人炒，做得最長嘅同事都係做咗兩年唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n返工第三日，我發現我個post一年已經走左5個同事。個個都係入黎做2-6個月，已經頂唔順resign。<br />\n<br />\n所以我公司為咗留我，免費送咗我去英國上堂一星期，條件係我兩年來唔辭職。<br />\n<br />\n但公司老闆實在太痴線同太冇道德，明明好想辭職，但因為俾人鎖約，如果自己辭職要賠一個月糧。<br />\n<br />\n雖然賠糧唔係一個問題，因為始終學咗嘅嘢係自己嘅。但明明睇住一個好冇道德嘅老闆，成功申請左商界顯關懷大獎，就好氣憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D錢唔應該俾啲hihi 賺<br />\n<br />\n唯一唔賠錢嘅方法係俾公司炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求搏炒方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c353d39961732b9afc7ed44b9836408369da309","tid":1819804,"uid":75550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"平時幾點收工？多唔多ot？"},{"pid":"048a02ab509e2891b87c3b776392e5f722c901d0","tid":1819804,"uid":118524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"返工上連登，仲要係佢面前上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0855e90a3400dbcbb430b4897038d84dabc62f4","tid":1819804,"uid":226082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c353d39961732b9afc7ed44b9836408369da309","tid":1819804,"uid":75550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"平時幾點收工？多唔多ot？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:54:35.000Z","msg":"10-10, 佢請我嗰時話10-6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8f890c134350db463d8654f2c5b14a2f3bea8a","tid":1819804,"uid":226082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc